  "statement": "Thread shows a plain-English read-time status. Inside a change's thread, the app SHALL show a plain-English \"what's happening\" status, derived at read-time from the change's state and conversation/journal. - *Acceptance:* Opening a change's thread shows a human-readable status sentence or short paragraph; it is computed on read, not from a stored periodic status post (the periodic auto-publish beat is a non-goal \u2014 see Non-goals)",
